163
00:11:08,047 --> 00:11:09,615
Yes, of course.

164
00:11:09,615 --> 00:11:10,850
Nonsense?

165
00:11:10,850 --> 00:11:11,851
Beat!

166
00:11:11,851 --> 00:11:14,454
