171
00:11:24,931 --> 00:11:27,600
I'm a money mind.

172
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,002
You're worse than me!

173
00:11:29,002 --> 00:11:32,605
Want to take my money?

174
00:11:32,605 --> 00:11:35,408
Beat you to death.

175
00:11:35,408 --> 00:11:37,807
- Beat! I really saw him.
- Did you?

176
00:11:37,807 --> 00:11:41,514
