You go first, I'll stay behind.

565
00:40:42,687 --> 00:40:43,779
Find another exit.

566
00:41:09,347 --> 00:41:10,541
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Mi.

567
00:41:16,888 --> 00:41:17,855
Swordsman Yen!

568
00:41:17,855 --> 00:41:18,823
Why have you come back?

569
00:41:18,823 --> 00:41:19,824
We can't get out of here!

570
00:41:19,824 --> 00:41:20,620
Old Evil has blocked the exit.

571
00:41:22,794 --> 00:41:25,592
You can't get out of here.

572
00:41:26,197 --> 00:41:27,289
Help me get an arrow.

573
00:41:27,999 --> 00:41:29,091
Full the bow.

574
00:41:30,201 --> 00:41:31,395
Let loose!

575
00:41:35,606 --> 00:41:36,698
Bad, we're not his match.

576
00:41:46,617 --> 00:41:48,386
Pull at him.
This is 1000-year old Evil.

577
00:41:48,386 --> 00:41:49,683
He may drain your soul away.

578
00:41:51,789 --> 00:41:52,778
Swordsman Yen!

579
00:42:08,306 --> 00:42:09,398
Concentrate!

580
00:42:09,741 --> 00:42:12,141
Recite!
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi.

581
00:42:13,911 --> 00:42:16,311
Lord Black, please let them go.

582
00:42:17,448 --> 00:42:23,421
Break the golden pagoda
and be my companion.

583
00:42:23,421 --> 00:42:25,616
Tsing, don't be taken in.

584
00:42:26,891 --> 00:42:28,586
Concentrate!
Recite!

585
00:42:29,494 --> 00:42:32,691
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi...

586
00:42:35,266 --> 00:42:36,460
Don't!

587
00:42:42,507 --> 00:42:43,701
I'll rescue you!

588
00:43:03,828 --> 00:43:05,022
Tsing!

589
00:43:11,435 --> 00:43:15,633
Yen Che-hsia, Ning Tsai-shen I'll take your lives.

590
00:43:22,146 --> 00:43:23,135
Don't!

591
00:43:26,150 --> 00:43:29,847
What's this? The sutra?

592
00:43:33,324 --> 00:43:34,392
You'd enough.

593
00:43:34,392 --> 00:43:35,586
I've to get rid of your damn evil.

594
00:43:53,077 --> 00:43:56,672
Damn old Evil!

595
00:43:57,582 --> 00:43:58,674
Swordsman Yen!

596
00:43:59,116 --> 00:44:01,311
The way's clear!
Help Swordsman Yen out!

597
00:44:07,124 --> 00:44:08,216
Swordsman Yen!

598
00:44:28,045 --> 00:44:30,343
Swordsman Yen, we're back to earth.

599
00:44:31,782 --> 00:44:33,384
Bad, it's dawn.

600
00:44:33,384 --> 00:44:34,476
Tsing's not yet here.

601
00:44:35,486 --> 00:44:36,783
Help her out.

602
00:44:43,828 --> 00:44:45,728
Swordsman Yen, lead a hand!

603
00:44:54,772 --> 00:44:55,761
Tsing!

604
00:44:56,474 --> 00:44:58,009
Keep her from the sunshine,

605
00:44:58,009 --> 00:45:00,603
or she may evaporate
and can't be reincarnated.

606
00:45:05,016 --> 00:45:08,315
Tsing,
come back to the golden pagoda!

607
00:45:14,492 --> 00:45:17,689
The sun is rising, I've to go!

608
00:45:20,898 --> 00:45:23,196
Tsing, be a good human being.

609
00:45:25,069 --> 00:45:27,271
I'll remember you always.

610
00:45:27,271 --> 00:45:30,172
Can't see you once before we apart.

611
00:45:31,042 --> 00:45:32,031
Take care!

612
00:45:38,149 --> 00:45:39,639
She's gone!

613
00:45:44,088 --> 00:45:50,994
I want to be together,

614
00:45:52,396 --> 00:46:00,895
till eternity.

615
00:46:04,575 --> 00:46:08,375
Tsing, I'll take you back.

616
00:46:34,038 --> 00:46:35,437
Wonder if she has been reincarnated.

617
00:46:35,973 --> 00:46:40,273
In there times,
an unlucky man may fare worse than a ghost.

618
00:46:46,017 --> 00:46:47,385
Ahead.

619
00:46:47,385 --> 00:46:48,477
Let's go.

620
00:46:52,223 --> 00:46:55,317
The path of life

621
00:46:55,843 --> 00:46:59,288
Are dreams, like the length of the path

622
00:47:00,264 --> 00:47:03,300
The storm on the way

623
00:47:03,300 --> 00:47:07,999
Pass by as you go along

624
00:47:08,372 --> 00:47:11,842
In the world

625
00:47:11,842 --> 00:47:16,313
How many ways can one dream?

626
00:47:16,313 --> 00:47:21,519
Looking for dream-like love

627
00:47:21,519 --> 00:47:25,922
And the path goes on

628
00:47:26,724 --> 00:47:33,823
Life is what dreams
and desires are made of

629
00:47:34,632 --> 00:47:37,735
Somewhere in the dream

630
00:47:37,735 --> 00:47:42,138
There are traces of tears

631
00:47:42,773 --> 00:47:46,210
Where to go to?

632
00:47:46,210 --> 00:47:50,010
To find where my heart wants to go

633
00:47:50,614 --> 00:47:55,820
The wind seems to sign in the dream,

634
00:47:55,820 --> 00:48:00,314
And the path and I go on
